      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "答案是有的，它叫一次一密，理论上完美保密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "intro",
