      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "它的秘密，藏在一个最简单的运算里，异或。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "xor",
      "line_id": "xor-1",
